Squirtle_voice_localization is a package that estimate sound direction according to microphone array reading

For detail introduction please check README in package

Bring up Squirtle voice localization will make you available to retrieve voice direction from it



How to bringup:

It's quite easy to use just plugin your arduino_collector and do:

$ roslaunch squirtle_voice_localization voice_localization_bringup.launch 

This will bring up both arduino node and localization node

 





